Sperry Capital has significant experience in planning and managing financings for municipal utilities in California, including water, waste water, solid waste and public power agencies.  Public agencies providing vital public services work with Sperry Capital advisory teams to analyze, develop and fund projects utilizing a variety of debt instruments for their capital projects.  Sperry Capital professionals are dedicated to establishing the right balance between borrowing and funding from current resources for our public agency clients.Utilities served:WaterWaste waterPublic powerSolid waste













