Many non-profit cor﻿p﻿orations have relied on Sperry Capital advisory teams for assistance in accessing the municipal bond market for their financing needs.  Municipal bonds traditionally provide a critical financing advantage fore these organizations faced with challenging credit and revenue structures.  A variety of institutions have called on Sperry Capital to develop a debt financing strategy, strengthen their credit profile and prepare for successful bond issuance.We have served the following segments:Cultural institutionsEducational facilitiesHealthcare facilitiesHousing - mobile home parks













